name: XII.II phasmito defectus
description:
"The phasmito defectus developed nice and shiny colors to attract attention and therefore reproduce in people's mind.
Not yet a threat, they sould not be underestimated and may actually look cute and friendly in order to try to conquer the world in a close future."

Part of the Encyclopedia Generativa Fluffosia project, a collection that classifies and describes ficional species.
